<p>突发！贵阳宝山南路发生地陷 <strong><span></span></strong></p>
<p><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">来源：贵州交通广播 <span></span></span></strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">编辑：吴艺舟</span></strong></span></p>
